OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly showers in the north and
OL,6,Feast, breaking out more widely during
OL,7,Fthe day, and turning locally heavy.
OL,8,FSome southern and western areas
OL,9,Fstaying mostly fine and dry, with some
OL,10,Fwarm sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers gradually fading this
OL,13,Fevening. Clear spells at first, but
OL,14,Fcloud will thicken in the east with
OL,15,Fdrizzly outbreaks. Strengthening winds
OL,16,Fin the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
